extends layout

block content
  h1 REST Word Counter
  p Count the ocurrences of words.

  h2 Usage

  h3 Count words on a text

  code POST #{fullUrl}

  h4 Parameters

  dl
    dt content
    dd The text content for searching

    dt search
    dd The word to search in content

  h4 Response

  h5 Headers

  code Content-type: application/json

  h5 Body

  pre: code.
    {
      "search": "foobar",
      "ocurrences": 42
    }


  h4 Test with <code>curl</code>

  code curl -d 'content=Lorem Ipsum&search=lorem' #{fullUrl}
